subSubSection.paragraph: Distribution. The species was hitherto known from Analamazaotra National Park [=Andasibe or Périnet], nearby situated Maromizaha [Réserve de Ressources Naturelles de Maromizaha], a locality 9 km South of Moramanga, Ambohiboatavo forest East of Mantasoa lake and Soa Camp in Anjozorobe. The new records are from forested areas East of Analamazaotra National Park.
